lated solutions, as well as installing, commissioning, and training services. In addition, the company offers industrial dryers; agro and coconut processing machineries; fruit and vegetable processing equipment; herbs and spices drying equipment; banana dehydration lines; suji, carbon pellets, and potato flakes dryers; and super absorbent polymers dryers. Further, it provides turnkey plant design and engineering services. Additionally, the company engages in the cultivation, manufacturing, and trading of tea. It exports its products. T & I Global Limited was founded in 1949 and is headquartered in Kolkata, India."}}